2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falec-musser-all-my-children-actoer-dead-at-50-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20hand%20out%20millions%20in%20lottery%20money%20%E2%80%94%20and%20am%20banned%20from%20playing.%20Here's%20why%20I'm%20not%20jealous%20of%20the%20winners.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%2C%20Joe%20and%20Jess%20Thwaite%2C%20smile%20against%20a%20verdant%20background%20as%20they%20spray%20a%20popped%20bottle%20of%20champagne%20to%20celebrate%20a%20%24232%20million%20lottery%20win%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6595533bec62ab5daf8037c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22713%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20and%20Jess%20Thwaite%20celebrate%20a%20%24232%20million%20lottery%20win%20in%202022.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Powell%2FCamelot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndy%20Carter's%20job%20is%20to%20hand%20out%20jackpots%20to%20lottery%20winners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20lottery%20employee%2C%20he's%20one%20of%20the%20few%20who%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20play.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20he%20doesn't%20envy%20the%20winners%20but%20is%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20their%20good%20luck.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Andy%20Carter%2C%20who%20advises%20major%20lottery%20winners%20for%20Camelot%2C%20the%20operator%20of%20the%20UK's%20National%20Lottery.%20His%20job%20involves%20processing%20payments%20and%20offering%20winners%20long-term%20support.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20people%20we%20deal%20with%20win%20about%20%C2%A31%20million%20(%241.25%20million).%20But%20we're%20dealing%20with%20people%20who%20win%20anything%20from%20%C2%A350%2C000%20up%20to%20%C2%A3190%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20for%20the%20lottery%20for%2017%20years%20and%20in%20that%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-lottery-winners-react-big-wins-unexpected-millionaires-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI've%20handed%20over%20in%20excess%20of%20%C2%A32%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I've%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20lottery%20winners%2C%20I%20haven't%20won%2C%20haha%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20can't%20even%20play.%20It's%20part%20of%20the%20licensing%20conditions%20for%20running%20a%20lottery%20in%20the%20UK%20that%20employees%20don't%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20good%20look%20if%20someone%20working%20for%20the%20lottery%20won%20the%20lottery.%20It%20would%20look%20a%20bit%20suspicious%20if%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20genuinely%20not%20jealous%20of%20the%20winners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20portrait%20of%20a%20smiling%20Andy%20Carter%2C%20a%20Winners'%20Advisor%20at%20UK%20lottery%20agency%20Camelot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656deeb70ec98e92f74b9d71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndy%20Carter%2C%20a%20Winners'%20Advisor%20at%20UK%20lottery%20agency%20Camelot.%3Cp%3EDylan%20Nolte%20%2B%20Anthony%20Highet%2FCamelot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20people%20ask%20me%20whether%20I%20get%20jealous%20of%20the%20people%20I%20give%20millions%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%20Because%20the%20issue%20with%20this%20job%20is%20it%20makes%20you%20think%20winning%20the%20lottery%20is%20normal%20and%20commonplace%2C%20and%20that's%20just%20not%20true.%20Winning%20the%20lottery%20is%20wacky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I've%20dealt%20with%20over%202%2C000%20lottery%20winners%2C%20and%20I've%20never%20dealt%20with%20anyone%20I%20know%20personally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20actually%20doing%20my%20job%20makes%20you%20think%20it's%20normal%20to%20win%2C%20when%20really%20it's%20so%20unusual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20and%20Helen%20Francis%20stand%20in%20a%20soccer%20stadium%2C%20popping%20a%20bottle%20of%20Champagne%20and%20holding%20a%20giant%20check%20for%20%C2%A31%20million%20as%20they%20celebrate%20their%20lottery%20win%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659553d6ab6f2ebb11f86431%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20and%20Helen%20Francis%20celebrate%20their%20%241.26%20million%20lottery%20win%20in%202022.%3Cp%3EHuw%20John%2FCamelot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20likes%20to%20chat%2C%20and%20associate%20themselves%20with%20funny%20stories%20and%20successes%2C%20I%20think%20that%20if%20you%20can't%20win%20then%20the%20very%20next%20best%20thing%20is%20speaking%20to%20people%20who%20%3Cem%3Edo%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewin%20every%20single%20day%20of%20your%20working%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20also%2C%20these%20people%20have%20come%20across%20their%20win%20through%20fair%20means.%20They%20haven't%20come%20to%20it%20through%20dubious%20means%20or%20underhand%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20just%20interesting%20to%20be%20around.%20It%20is%20fascinating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20just%20be%20that%20it's%20part%20of%20the%20DNA%20that%20you%20need%20to%20do%20this%20job.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20people%20in%20my%20team%2C%20they%20will%20all%20feel%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20a%20myth%20that%20lottery%20wins%20always%20make%20people%20miserable%2C%20though%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20misconception%20people%20have%20about%20lottery%20winners%20is%20that%20everyone%20goes%20out%20and%20blows%20their%20money.%20It%20couldn't%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20public%20are%20overwhelmingly%20very%2C%20very%20conservative%20with%20their%20lo