ted%20his%20over%201340-mile%20road%20trip.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dennis%20Wang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20YouTuber%20took%20a%20Cybertruck%20on%20a%201340-mile%20roadtrip%20and%20posted%20it%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDennis%20Wang%20said%20he%20enjoyed%20the%20Cybertruck's%20spacious%20design%20but%20ran%20into%20some%20hiccups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-price-release-event-delivery-truck-live-updates-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20began%20deliveries%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20electric%20pickup%20truck%20on%20November%2030.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYouTuber%20Dennis%20Wang%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20drivers%20to%20document%20a%20cross-country%20road%20trip%20in%20the%20much-hyped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-truck-cybertruck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20weeks%20after%20the%20first%20vehicles%20were%20shipped%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20Foundation%20Series%20version%20of%20the%20truck%20was%20released%2C%20Wang%20and%20his%20friend%2C%20took%20it%20on%20a%2027-hour%20road%20trip%20from%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20to%20Joshua%20Tree%20National%20Park%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%2C%20who%20runs%20DennisCW%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40DennisCW%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20focuses%20on%20Tesla%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20wanted%20to%20put%20the%20Cybertruck%20through%20its%20paces%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20the%20ride.%20But%20he%20ran%20into%20some%20issues%20along%20the%20way%20%E2%80%94%20including%20difficulties%20with%20charging%20and%20a%20glitch%20in%20Tesla's%20infotainment%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20most%20comfortable%20Tesla%20that%20I've%20owned%2C%20but%20in%20terms%20of%20efficiency%20it%20was%20definitely%20lacking%20in%20range%20and%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20a%20lot%20along%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wang%2C%20who%20said%20he's%20driven%20all%20four%20other%20Tesla%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FM_5CtSwPNiY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Taking%20the%20CYBERTRUCK%20on%20a%20MASSIVE%20ROADTRIP%20%7C%20Charging%20was%20TOUGH%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cybertruck%20Foundation%20Series%20has%20an%20estimated%20range%20of%20320%20miles%20on%20its%20all-wheel%20drive%20option.%20But%2C%20Wang%20said%2C%20at%20times%20it%20felt%20that%20range%20was%20cut%20in%20half.%20The%20pair%20stopped%2012%20times%20during%20the%201%2C340-mile%20trip%2C%20which%20rounds%20out%20to%20just%20over%20110%20miles%20between%20charges%2C%20and%20Wang%20said%20they%20stopped%20every%20one%20to%20two%20hours%20to%20recharge.%20While%20the%20pair%20took%20turns%20driving%20straight%20through%20the%20night%2C%20the%20stops%20turned%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%2020-hour%20road%20trip%20into%20a%2027-hour%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20attributes%20the%20inefficiencies%20in%20range%20to%20the%20cooler%20temperatures%20in%20Texas%20and%20his%20tendency%20to%20speed.%20He%20said%20he's%20seen%20improved%20range%20since%20driving%20the%20car%20in%20California's%20more%20temperate%20climate.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20closing%20the%20tonneau%2C%20the%20cover%20that%20spans%20the%20back%20of%20the%20truck%2C%20helped%20improve%20the%20Cybertruck's%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20isn't%20the%20first%20to%20point%20out%20some%20potential%20issues%20in%20the%20Cybertruck's%20estimated%20range.%20Last%20week%2C%20%26quot%3BOut%20of%20Spec%20Reviews%26quot%3B%20performed%20an%20unofficial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-range-test-real-world-youtube-less-than-advertised-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighway%20range%20test%20on%20a%20Cybertruck%20%3C%2Fa%3EFoundation%20Series%20vehicle%20that%20showed%20the%20vehicle%20clocked%20in%20at%20just%20254%20miles%20of%20range%20when%20driven%20from%20a%20full%20charge%20until%20the%20battery%20died%2C%20only%20about%2080%25%20of%20its%20estimated%20range.%20Wang%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20said%20he%20tended%20to%20charge%20the%20vehicle%20from%20a%2010-30%25%20range%20up%20to%20a%2070-80%25%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20factors%20can%20impact%20an%20electric%20car's%20range%2C%20including%20tires%2C%20weight%20load%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20cold%20weather%20conditions.%20A%202023%20study%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.recurrentauto.com%2Fresearch%2Fwinter-ev-range-loss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERecurrent%20Auto%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20cited%20by%20Bloomberg%20found%20that%20many%20EVs%20lost%20about%2030%25%20of%20their%20range%20in%20temperatures%20below%20freezing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20unexpected%20difficulty%3A%20charging%20the%20car.%20When%20Wang%20stopped%20to%20use%20Tesla's%20Superchargers%2C%20many%20didn't%20appear%20to%20be%20designed%20with%20the%20Cybertruck's%20larger%20size%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20had%20to%20back%20up%20as%20far%20as%20possible%20to%20the%20parking%20stop%20for%20the%20cable%20to%20reach%2C%20and%20sometimes%20the%20cable%20was%20barely%20long%20enough%20to%20plug%20into%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221759%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wang%20charged%20at%2012%20different%20Superchargers%20along%20the%20roadtrip.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F