%2Fworld-latin-america-67947333%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20victims%20was%20reportedly%20Tou%20Ger%20Xiong%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20Asian-American%20comedian%20and%20activist%20living%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20per%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2050-year-old%20was%20kidnapped%20and%20killed%20while%20on%20vacation%20in%20Colombia%20at%20the%20end%20of%20November%20after%20he%20went%20on%20a%20date%20with%20a%20woman%20he%20had%20met%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOften%20the%20gangs%20employ%20beautiful%20women%20with%20alluring%20features%20to%20lure%20in%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andr%C3%A9s%20Nieto%2C%20a%20crime%20and%20security%20expert%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20per%20The%20Guardian.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%20believes%20the%20deaths%20involved%20involuntary%20drugging%20overdoses%20or%20suspected%20homicides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20victims%20had%20been%20using%20online%20dating%20apps%2C%20prompting%20authorities%20to%20warn%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20meeting%20strangers%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-colombian-cartels-work-former-undercover-agent-2023-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColombian%20gangs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20known%20to%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-there-such-a-thing-as-truth-serum-2014-10%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escopolamine%2C%20a%20drug%20derived%20from%20nightshade%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fjan%2F11%2Fcolombia-dating-apps-tourist-deaths%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erender%20their%20victims%20helpless%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebefore%20robbing%20them%2C%20the%20Guardian%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20embassy%20describes%20a%20pattern%20where%20criminals%20exploit%20dating%20apps%20to%20lure%20victims%20to%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20bars