20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6597ea381c5c7b8c9a0e39f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221154%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarti%20Stelling%20has%20worked%20part-time%20at%20Booths%20for%20five%20years.%3Cp%3EMarti%20Stelling%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBooths%2C%20a%20UK%20supermarket%20chain%2C%20recently%20removed%20almost%20all%20its%20self-service%20checkouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECustomer%20assistant%C2%A0Marti%20Stelling%20shares%20how%20the%20move%20has%20affected%20her%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20end%20of%20self-service%20checkouts%20does%20have%20some%20drawbacks%20for%20employees%2C%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Marti%20Stelling%2C%20a%20customer%20assistant%20at%20Booths.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20worked%20at%20Booths%20as%20a%20part-time%20customer%20assistant%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooths%20is%20a%20high-end%20supermarket%20in%20the%20UK.%20I%20work%20there%20during%20all%20my%20vacations%20from%20studying%20and%20I%20like%20returning%20because%20it's%20a%20people-centric%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20really%20big%20emphasis%20on%20customer%20service.%20We%20have%20greeters%20on%20the%20doors%20and%20a%20caf%C3%A9.%20When%20you%20go%20to%20a%20Booths%2C%20it's%20about%20the%20experience%20beyond%20just%20getting%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20cash%20registers%2C%20we're%20encouraged%20to%20start%20a%20conversation%20with%20customers%20and%20make%20sure%20they've%20got%20everything%20they%20want.%20When%20disabled%20customers%20come%20in%2C%20we%20walk%20around%20with%20them%20and%20carry%20their%20baskets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENo%20more%20self-checkouts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAligning%20with%20those%20values%20is%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20that%20Booths%20has%20just%20removed%20all%20self-service%20checkouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20store%20in%20Rippon%2C%20North%20Yorkshire%2C%20where%20I%20work%2C%20we%20got%20rid%20of%20the%20self-service%20checkouts%20in%20February%202021.%20Now%20they've%20done%20it%20across%20all%20stores%20apart%20from%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20extra%20cash%20registers%20were%20put%20in%20to%20replace%20the%20self-service%20ones.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20kiosk%20for%20lottery%20tickets%20and%20cigarettes%20that%20can%20be%20used%20if%20you%20have%20under%2010%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20you%20have%20to%20have%20more%20staff%20on%20than%20if%20you%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20self-service%20machines%2C%20but%20you%20always%20had%20to%20have%20someone%20manning%20the%20self-service%20tills%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%20sometimes%20people%20skip%20a%20few%20items%20when%20scanning%20their%20own%20shopping%20through.%20It's%20become%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20joke%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20to%20see%20%26quot%3Bhow%20cheap%20you%20can%20make%20your%20shop%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20lots%20of%20supermarkets%20make%20a%20loss%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECustomers%20had%20a%20mixed%20reaction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20some%20negative%20reactions.%20People%20who%20just%20wanted%20to%20grab%20something%20quickly%20were%20annoyed%20about%20their%20self-checkouts%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20a%20year%2C%20customers%20would%20come%20in%20and%20ask%20where%20they%20had%20gone%2C%20claiming%20they%20were%20there%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20always%20seem%20to%20take%20it%20out%20on%20the%20people%20who%20don't%20make%20the%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20get%20annoyed%20about%20long%20queues%20in%20busy%20times%20and%20blame%20us%2C%20but%20we%20can%20only%20do%20our%20job%2C%20and%20the%20self-checkouts%20being%20removed%20is%20aimed%20at%20creating%20better%20customer%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Martin%20Stelling%20Booths%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65981d4b6979d7371820bbc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Booths%20store%20where%20Marti%20works%20has%20removed%20all%20self-service%20checkouts.%3Cp%3EMarti%20Stelling%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20really%20liked%20the%20change%2C%20and%20many%20are%20happy%20to%20see%20someone%20face-to-face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20our%20customers%20are%20older%20and%20find%20self-service%20machines%20really%20confusing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Rippon%2C%20we%20have%20quite%20a%20big%20Sainsbury's%20store%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0another%20UK%20supermarket.%20They've%20recently%20removed%20almost%20all%20of%20their%20cash%20registers.%20From%20speaking%20to%20my%20grandma%20and%20her%20friends%2C%20they%20are%20really%20unhappy%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20old%20person%2C%20going%20to%20the%20shop%20and%20speaking%20to%20an%20attendant%20might%20be%20the%20only%20person%20they%20speak%20to%20all%20day.%20If%20all%20they%20want%20to%20do%20is%20chat%20and%20spend%20an%20afternoon%20in%20our%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20they%20are%20welcome%20at%20Booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20Booths%20will%20take%20away%20a%20lot%20of%20Sainsbury's%20customers%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWithout%20self-checkouts%2C%20it's%20harder%20to%20buy%20one%20or%20two%20items%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20here%20prefer%20cash%20registers%20because%20its%20more%20interactive%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20standing%20around%20waiting%20to%20help%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManning%20the%20checkout%20has%20always%20been%20part%20of%20the%20job.%20I%20don't%20find%20the%20work%20busier%20than%20when%20we%20had%20self-service%20machines%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20drawback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20had%20self-serving%20machines%2C%20it%20was%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20grab%20one%20or%20two%20items%20quickly.%20Now%2C%20it%20takes%20slightly%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20breaks%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20warehouse%20upstairs%20to%20clock%20out%20before%20coming%20down%20and%20buying%20something%20for%20lunch.%20During%20a%20four-hour%20shift%2C%20we%20only%20have%20fifteen%20minutes.%20If%20it's%20a%20busy%20period%2C%20you%20spend%20your%20entire%20break%20queuing%20behind%20customers%20to%20grab%20a%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221078%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marti%20Stelling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659824466979d7371820c1a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20removal%20of%20self-service%20checkouts%20has%20a%20negative%20side%20for%20staff%2C%20says%20Marti%20Stelling.%3Cp%3EMarti%20Stelling%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ERetail%20technology%20could%20catch%20up%20to%20Booths%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBooths%20is%20definitely%20going%20the%20opposite%20way%20to%20most%20places%20and%20it's%20true%20that%20we%20are%20somewhat%20slow%20to%20adapt%20to%20technology%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20technology%20is%20great%2C%20but%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20people%20there%20to%20help%20guide%20people%20through%20the%20changes%2C%20especially%20older%20people%20like%20my%20gran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20majority%20of%20shops%20are%20moving%20toward%20automated%20machines%20rather%20than%20prioritizing%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20Booths%20can%20survive%20the%20way%20they%20are%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20I%20suspect%20the%20company%20is%20going%20to%20have%20to%20adapt%20to%20these%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbooths-grocery-chain-removed-self-service-checkouts-staff-prefer-it-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705225861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6597ed1f