p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELet%20us%20take%20a%20look%20at%20who%20is%20Crown%20Prince%20Frederik%2C%20Denmark's%20king-in-waiting%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Born%20in%201968%2C%20the%20crown%20prince's%20full%20name%20is%20Frederik%20Andr%C3%A9%20Henrik%20Christian.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20child%20of%20Queen%20Margrethe%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Prince%20Henrik%2C%20who%20died%20in%202018.%C2%A0%20Prince%20Frederik's%20younger%20brother%2C%20Prince%20Joachim%2C%20was%20born%20in%201969.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20As%20per%20CNN%2C%20the%20crown%20prince%20in%201995%20became%20the%20first%20Danish%20royal%20to%20gain%20a%20master's%20degree.%20After%20pursuing%20a%20master's%20from%20Aarhus%20University%2C%20his%20political%20science%20studies%20included%20a%20year%20abroad%2C%20at%20Harvard%2C%20where%20he%20was%20enrolled%20under%20the%20pseudonym%20of%20Frederik%20Henriksen%20-%20a%20nod%20to%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Fredrik%20is%20fluent%20in%20French%2C%20English%20and%20German.%20As%20per%20Aljazeera%2C%20he%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Evangelical%20Lutheran%20Church%20of%20Denmark%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20Danish%20National%20Church).%20It%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20the%20Danish%20royal%20family%2C%20especially%20for%20reigning%20monarchs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Frederik%20is%20a%20Frogman%20in%20the%20Royal%20Danish%20Navy's%20special%20force%2C%20whose%20training%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20toughest.%20The%20crown%20prince%20has%20run%20six%20marathons%20and%20participated%20in%20a%20four-month%2C%202%2C795-km%20(1%2C737-mile)%20dogsled%20expedition%20in%20northern%20Greenland%2C%20which%20is%20a%20sovereign%20territory%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Frederik%20has%20been%20known%20as%20the%20Crown%20Prince%20of%20Denmark%20since%20the%20age%20of%20three.%20From%20Sunday%20he%20will%20leave%20that%20title%20behind%2C%20taking%20over%20as%20King%20Frederik%20X%2C%20sovereign%20o