%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-ally-hints-at-poland-as-next-in-ukraine-war-raises-nato-implications%2Famp_articleshow%2F106830914.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Allegedly%20Kills%20Boyfriend's%20Child%20By%20Feeding%20Her%20Screws%2C%20Batteries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Pennsylvania%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20fatally%20poisoning%20her%20boyfriend's%20toddler%20by%20feeding%20her%20batteries%2C%20screws%20and%20nail%20polish%20remover.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F12%2Fnews%2Firis-alfera-allegedly-killed-by-dads-girlfriend-aleisia-owens%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Aleisia%20Owens%20was%20arrested%20on%20Thursday%20for%20the%20suspected%20homicide%20of%20Iris%20Rita%20Alfera%2C%20last%20year%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Aleisia%20was%20arrested%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.attorneygeneral.gov%2Ftaking-action%2Flawrence-county-woman-charged-with-killing-one-year-old-girl-with-fatal-dose-of-acetone-following-prior-incidents-of-abuse%2F%5C%22%3EPennsylvania%20Attorney%20General%20Michelle%20Henry%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20that%20an%20autopsy%20determined%20the%20child's%20death%20was%20caused%20due%20to%20fatal%20levels%20of%20acetone%20in%20her%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20revealed%20that%20the%2020-year-old%20woman%20researched%20the%20harmful%20effects%20the%20items%20could%20have%20on%20a%20child%20before%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.attorneygeneral.gov%2Ftaking-action%2Flawrence-county-woman-charged-with-killing-one-year-old-girl-with-fatal-dose-of-acetone-following-prior-incidents-of-abuse%2F%5C%22%3EAttorney%20General%20Henry%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20details%20of%20this%20case%20are%20heartbreaking.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20fathom%20someone%20taking%20deliberate%20steps%20to%20harm%20a%20completely%20helpless%20child%2C%20and%20then%20mislead%20investigators%20about%20what%20happened.%20The%20investigation%20shows%20that%2C%20for%20months%2C%20the%20defendant%20conducted%20meticulous%20research%20on%20how%20certain%20substances%20harm%20children.%20She%20then%20allegedly%20acted%20on%20her%20findings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2025%2C%202023%2C%20the%2020-year-old%20was%20with%20Iris'%20father%20Bailey%20Jacoby%2C%20when%20he%20left%20the%20house%20to%20go%20to%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20time%2C%20Mr%20Jacoby%20received%20a%20call%20from%20Ms%20Owens%20that%20something%20was%20wrong%20with%20his%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20obtained%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wpxi.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Farrest-made-death-new-castle-toddler%2FDSERHFACTNH6BABFO4MG2RYXSA%2F%5C%22%3EWPXI%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Bailey%20Jacob%20rushed%20to%20the%20New%20Castle%20home%20only%20to%20find%20his%20baby%20unresponsive.%20He%20immediately%20called%20911.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20this%2C%20the%2018-month-old%20toddler%20was%20rushed%20to%20UPMC%20Jameson%20Hospital%20in%20New%20Castle%20for%20treatment.%20However%2C%20roughly%20one%20hour%20away%2C%20she%20was%20airlifted%20to%20UPMC%20Children's%20Hospital%20in%20Pittsburgh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20sadly%2C%20four%20days%20later%20Iris%20died%20due%20to%20organ%20failure.%20Iris%20lived%20with%20her%20mother%20Emily%20Alfera%20and%20her%20grandparents%20while%20her%20father%2C%20Mr%20Jacoby%2C%20had%20only%20visitation%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20revealed%20that%20Ms%20Aleisia%20told%20police%20that%20the%20girl%20had%20hit%20her%20head%20after%20she%20%E2%80%9Ccramped%20up%E2%80%9D%20and%20fell%20off%20her%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20autopsy%20report%20exhibited%20that%20the%2018-month-old%20baby%20ingested%20numerous%20%E2%80%9Cwater%20beads%2C%E2%80%9D%20along%20with%20b