%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fr-ashwin-doesnt-deserve-place-in-white-ball-cricket-india-need-hardik-pandya-yuvraj-singh%2Farticleshow%2F106828013.cms%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Yuvraj%20was%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20how%20good%20Ashwin%20is%20as%20a%20red-ball%20cricketer%2C%20but%20the%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20because%20of%20what%20the%20limited-overs%20formats%20demand%20from%20a%20player.%20For%20Yuvi%2C%20Ashwin%20is%20a%20great%20bowler%20but%20doesn't%20bring%20much%20with%20the%20bat%20and%20in%20the%20field%20in%20white-ball%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshwin%20is%20a%20great%20bowler%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20deserves%20a%20place%20in%20ODIs%20and%20T20s.%20He%20is%20very%20good%20with%20the%20ball%2C%20but%20what%20does%20he%20bring%20with%20the%20bat%3F%20Or%20as%20a%20fielder%3F%20In%20the%20Test%20team%2C%20yes%2C%20he%20should%20be%20there.%20But%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20deserves%20a%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Yuvraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20and%20Ashwin%20were%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20that%20won%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%202011.%20Time%20and%20again%2C%20Ashwin%20has%20spoken%20quite%20highly%20of%20Yuvraj's%20contributions%20to%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20health%20crisis%20he%20went%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20videos%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Ashwin%20had%20revealed%20how%20shocked%20he%20was%20upon%20knowing%20that%20he%20had%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYuvi%20used%20to%20cough%2C%20and%20he%20used%20to%20cough%20vehemently.%20I%20used%20to%20think%20that%20it%20is%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20game%20and%20he%20is%20coughing%20it%20off%20and%20he%20used%20to%20cough%20in%20the%20middle.%20Literally%2C%20nobody%20had%20any%20idea%2C%20at%20least%20from%20the%20junior%20segment%20of%20the%20team%20that%20he%20was%20suffering%20from%20a%20serious%2