e%20and%20comedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98fast%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20title%20refers%20to%20Karwa%20Chauth.%20The%20novel%20is%20based%20in%20Bangalore%E2%80%99s%20Shivajinagar%2C%20in%20one%20galli%20where%20everyone%20knows%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20or%20think%20they%20do%2C%20until%20a%20murder%20takes%20place%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20fast.%20The%20murdered%20man%E2%80%99s%20wife%20had%20broken%20her%20%E2%80%98KC%E2%80%99%20fast%20earlier%20that%20day%2C%20leading%20to%20talk%20from%20some%20that%20she%20caused%20his%20death%2C%20while%20others%20scoff%20at%20that%20theory%20and%20the%20superstition%20it%20involves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20like%20the%20darkness%20in%20that%20juxtaposition%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20man%20being%20murdered%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20fast%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chauhan%20said%20at%20the%20Kerala%20Literature%20Festival%20on%20Saturday%20(January%2013).%20Chauhan%20says%20she%20thinks%20that%20Karwa%20Chauth%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblind%20superstition%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20spread%20across%20the%20country%20because%20of%20its%20portrayals%20in%20Bollywood%2C%20and%20the%20differing%20viewpoints%20on%20the%20subject%20come%20across%20from%20the%20characters%20of%20her%20book.%20%E2%80%9CI%20like%20putting%20irreverent%20dialogues%20in%20my%20characters%E2%80%99%20mouths%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20book%20is%20very%20much%20a%20detective%20story%20set%20in%20a%20micro-locality%2C%20changes%20that%20India%20has%20seen%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20more%20have%20seeped%20in.%20A%20young%2C%20successful%20Muslim%20actor%20is%20a%20suspect%2C%20and%20TV%20news%20channels%20immediately%20bay%20for%20his%20blood%20and%20run%20hashtags%20that%20call%20him%20a%20murderer.%20%E2%80%9CA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chauhan%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20Muslim%20identity%20would%20not%20have%20been%20so%20primary.%E2%80%9D%20But%20given%20the%20realities%20of%20today%2C%20she%20felt%20she%20had%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20authentic%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChauhan%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20her%20book%2C%20censorship%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20and%20more.%20Edited%20excerpts%20from%20the%20interview%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20now%20your%20second%20murder%20mystery.%20What%20led%20to%20the%20change%20in%20genre%3F%20Is%20the%20writing%20process%20very%20different%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20more%20mathematical.%20Because%20in%20a%20romance%20you%20can%20pretty%20much%20start%20off%20and%20see%20where%20you%20go%2C%20but%20here%20the%20plotting%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20careful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20need%20to%20know%20who%20did%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20know%20who%20did%20it%2C%20and%20you%20need%20to%20leave%20enough%20clues%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20hide%20them%20also.%20And%20the%20timeline%E2%80%A6%20there%E2%80%99s%20that.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20plotted%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20more%20scaffolding%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20show%20once%20the%20skin%20is%20on%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20my%20reading%20of%20all%20your%20novels%2C%20across%20genres%2C%20there%20is%20an%20underlying%20subtle%2C%20humorous%20social%20commentary.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20much%20based%20in%20our%20present%2C%20both%20very%20locally%20and%20nationally.%20What%20drew%20you%20to%20that%20style%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20I%20write.%20I%20love%20observing%20this%20stuff%2C%20and%20recording%20it%2C%20and%20laughing%20about%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20sometimes%20angry%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99m%20mostly%20affectionate%2C%20I%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20our%20current%20socio-political%20realities%2C%20where%20there%20are%20very%20present%20forms%20of%20censorship%2C%20like%20recently%20things%20being%20taken%20off%20Netflix%20for%20instance%2C%20affect%20writers%20like%20you%20who%20have%20a%20social%20commentary%20in%20their%20writing%2C%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20main%20feature%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20sad%2C%20I%20think.%20It%E2%80%99s%20depressing.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20on%20to%20X%20%E2%80%93%20you%20see%20two%20posts%20about%20Gaza%2C%20or%20two%20posts%20about%20a%20movie%20like%20this%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20the%20kind%20of%20hate%20people%20put.%20If%20you%20scroll%20through%20the%20comments%2C%20and%20you%20see%20that%20everyone%20clearly%20seems%20to%20think%20that%20this%20is%20the%20correct%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20so%20uninformed.%20When%20did%20we%20say%20that%20Kshatriyas%20don%E2%80%99t%20eat%20meat%2C%20for%20heaven%E2%80%99s%20sake.%20And%20what%20about%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBajrangi%20Bhaijaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20came%20out%20in%202016.%20So%20if%20you%20start%20going%20down%20that%20rabbit%20hole%20you%20really%20lose%20it%2C%20I%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20think%20this%20is%20the%20time%20to%20go%20not%20ostrich-y%2C%20but%20somewhere%20hold%20on%20to%20your%20beliefs.%20Because%20otherwise%20the%20world%20will%20convince%20you%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20the%20crazy%20one.%20It%E2%80%99s%20nuts.%20It%20just%20feels%20sad%2C%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20incomplete%20temple%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20consecrated.%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20disconnect.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20I%E2%80%99ve%20stopped%20trying%20to%20convince%20people%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20exhausted.%20So%20I%E2%80%99ll%20save%20my%20energy%20and%20I%E2%80%99ll%20write%20about%20it%20gently%2C%20in%20my%20own%20way%2C%20and%20do%20what%20I%20can%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20has%20this%20affected%20the%20literature%20and%20popular%20culture%20landscape%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%2C%20of%20course%20it%20has.%20People%20are%20pandering%20to%20the%20reigning%20mentality%20in%20all%20sorts%20of%20ways%2C%20some%20subtle%20ways%20and%20some%20not-so-subtle%20ways%2C%20and%20other%20people%20are%20being%20emboldened.%20In%20the%20dark%20places%20of%20your%20mind%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20slap%20your%20girlfriend%2C%20now%20you%E2%80%99ll%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20fine%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it.%20We%E2%80%99re%20loosening%20the%20leash%20on%20monsters%20of%20all%20sorts%2C%20to%20crazy%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20also%20write%20regular%20columns%20in%20addition%20to%20your%20novels.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20write%20for%20a%20good%20Malayali%20publication%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0magazine.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20writing%20it%20for%20almost%2015%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20ever%20plan%20on%20doing%20a%20longer%20non-fiction%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20like%20to%20inform%20my%20fiction%20with%20whatever%20is%20happening%20rather%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20your%20works%20have%20already%20been%20turned%20in%20movies%20and%20series%2C%20others%20are%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20ACP%20Bhavani%20is%20coming%20to%20Netflix%20soon.%20Do%20you%20work%20with%20them%20in%20that%20process%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20not%20really.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20realised%20from%20my%20work%20in%20advertising%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20have%20no%20control.%20So%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20point.%20So%20I%E2%80%99m%20like%20here%20take%20it%2C%20give%20me%20the%20moolah%2C%20and%20do%20what%20you%20can.%20And%20I%E2%80%99ll%20leave%20it%20at%20that.%20Because%20I%E2%80%99ll%20just%20be%20a%20nuisance%2C%20and%20a%20nuisance%20without%20power.%20So%20there%E2%80%99s%20not%20point.%20And%20these%20are%20all%20directors%20I%20trust.%C2%A0Homi%20Adajania%20is%20directing%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMurder%20Mubarak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20really%20good%20director.%20So%20I%E2%80%99m%20like%20okay%2C%20you%20do%20what%20you%20like.%20And%20I%20love%20the%20casting%20%E2%80%93%20I%20think%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%20%5Bas%20ACP%20Bhavani%5D%20is%20great%20casting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20now%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20sitting%20on%20my%20butt.%20I%E2%80%99m%20closing%20a%20couple%20of%20movie%20deals%2C%20so%20I%E2%80%99m%20in%20that%20very%20finance%20mode%20for%20now.%20I%20guess%20I%E2%80%99ll%20start%20writing%20again%20in%20March%2C%20and%20then%20I%E2%80%99ll%20see%20what%20I%E2%80%99ll%20write.%20If%20this%20movie%2C%20%3Cem%3EMurder%20Mubarak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20does%20well%2C%20then%20maybe%20one%20more%20ACP%20will%20hunt%20again.%20Or%20if%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%20well%2C%20then%20maybe%20I%E2%80%99ll%20put%20a%20little%20more%20%E2%80%98rom%E2%80%99%20into%20my%20%E2%80%98crom%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlready%20the%20second%20one%20does%20have%20more%20romance%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYa%2C%20I%20know.%20Also%20because%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20grief%20on%20the%20first%20book%2C%20they%20said%20I%E2%80%99ve%20ruined%20the%20romance.%20So%20I%20said%20okay%20now%20the%20romance%20is%20clean%20now%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%C2%A0Fast%20and%20the%20Dead%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705199431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13195552%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-7.54.47-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fhold-on-to-your-beliefs-or-the-world-will-convince-you-youre-the-crazy-one-anuja-chauhan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anuja%20Chauhan%20spoke%20to%20The%20Wire%20about%20her%20detective%20fiction%2C%20censorship%20in%20today's%20India%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%2