.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F2024%2F01%2F11%2Fpannun-case-us-objects-to-providing-defence-material-to-nikhil-gupta-till-his-appearance-in-ny-court.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChabrowe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CMost%20critically%2C%20the%20defendant%20continues%20(to%20be)%20interrogated%20by%20US%20officials%2C%20after%20the%20indictment%2C%20where%20his%20uninformed%20counsel%20has%20no%20ability%20to%20secure%20his%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccordingly%2C%20this%20court%20should%20order%20the%20government%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20defence%20discovery%20request%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20request%20for%20%E2%80%98discovery%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20a%20request%20to%20the%20prosecution%20to%20share%20certain%20case%20materials%20and%20evidence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao%2Fjustice-101%2Fdiscovery%5C%22%3Eahead%20of%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Judge%20Marrero%20had%20on%20Monday%20(January%208)%20given%20the%20government%20three%20days%20to%20respond%20to%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20produce%20discovery%20upon%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20in%20court%20and%20that%20he%20was%20not%20entitled%20to%20discovery%20until%20then%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20denied%20that%20Gupta%20was%20repeatedly%20interrogated%20by%20US%20officials%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20adding%20that%20Gupta%20and%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20had%20only%20met%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20voluntarily%20spoke%20to%20authorities%20in%20their%20first%20meeting%20and%20declined%20to%20be%20interviewed%20upon%20their%20second%20meeting%2C%20PTI%20cited%20the%20US%20government%20as%20arguing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20plea%20filed%20in%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20behalf%20claims%20that%20the%20circumstan