ation%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetail%20rice%20prices%20rose%20by%2012.33%25%20in%20December%2C%20compared%20to%2011.81%25%20in%20November.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20measures%20to%20ban%20white%20rice%20exports%20and%20impose%20a%2020%25%20export%20duty%20on%20par-boiled%20rice%20contributed%20to%20the%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frising-thali-cost-muted-fmcg-growth-booming-luxury-sales-why-the-k-shaped-recovery-still-stands%5C%22%3ERising%20Thali%20Cost%2C%20Muted%20Fmcg%20Growth%2C%20Booming%20Luxury%20Sales%3A%20Why%20the%20K-Shaped%20Recovery%20Still%20Stands%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COutlook%20for%20the%20inflation%20for%20certain%20items%20like%20rice%2C%20wheat%20and%20pulses%20remains%20somewhat%20vulnerable%2C%20given%20the%20estimated%20fall%20in%20annual%20kharif%20production%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20year-on-year%20lag%20in%20the%20ongoing%20rabi%20sowing%20season%20amid%20El%20Nino%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aditi%20Nayar%2C%20chief%20economist%2C%20ICRA%2C%20told%20the%20business%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumer%20price%20index%20(CPI)-based%20inflation%20rose%205.69%25%2C%20its%20fastest%20pace%20in%20four%20months%20in%20December%2C%20the%20statistics%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20industrial%20output%20growth%20fell%20to%20an%20eight-month%20low%20of%202.4%25%20in%20November.%20The%20previous%20low%20of%20IIP%20(Index%20of%20Industrial%20Production)%20growth%20was%20recorded%20at%201.9%25%20growth%20in%20March%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Findustrial-production-growth-decelerates-to-8-month-low-of-24-in-november-2846740%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520factory%2520output%2520growth%2520measured%2Cper%2520cent%2520in%2520November%25202022.%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520previous%2520low%2520of%2520IIP%2Ccent%2520growth%2520in%2520March%25202023.%5C%22%3Er